cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR 

The paper is about person re-identification using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses training tricks and network structures, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method on a dataset, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the consistency of metric and classification losses, which is related to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
